Title: How to Capture and Share a Visual Thought.

Preference will be given to sessions that incorporate voices from diverse backgrounds and/or different global communities. How does your session accomplish this?

I've created a visual guide to accompany the session, and I'll partner up groups of people with a common working language. The majority of the session will be participatory and involve creating shareable assets, so this should work well.

