A co-operative is an  autonomous association of persons united voluntarily to meet their  common economic, social, and cultural needs and aspirations through a  jointly-owned and democratically-controlled enterprise.

Let's do a little remix:

The Commons are artefacts openly licensed by an autonomous association of persons. They use open licensing to meet their common economic, social, and cultural needs and aspirations through a jointly-owned and democratically-controlled system of resources.

