Library Manager at Greenpeace International  October 2007 – Present (8 years 1 month)
Budget and planning responsibility for a library and media services department tasked to support a global communications strategy across all platforms and campaigns. Development and implementation of practical policy guidelines for acquisition and international distribution of visual media assets, Managing key relationships with internal and external partners /stakeholders in supporting this and other Greenpeace policies. 
Broadcast Services Manager Metro Broadcast Ltd  August 2001 – October 2007 (6 years 3 months)
